Larry Ward (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Larry_Ward_(actor) 0 Larry Ward (October 3, 1924 – February 16, 1985) was an American actor who appeared in many films and television series. He was sometimes credited under the name Ward Gaynor. Larry_Ward ( October_3_,_1924 – February_16_,_1985 ) was an_American_actor who appeared in many_films_and_television_series .
